      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "NORTH YAKIMA, Dec. %. -\nThe following telegram, signed by\nthe imayor and editors of Yakima\nand a few other prominent citizens,\nwas forwarded to Representative\nJones, denying the report that the\npeople of Yakima are with Cover\nnor Mead in his attitude on the\nCarey land selections:\n\n\nGovernor Mead denies that the\npress and the people in Yakima and\nKittitas valleys are particularly\nunanimous for the withdrawal of\nthe states claims to the Carey\nlands. He is mistaken. The people\nwant the Carey selections with.\ndrawn and every other obstacle to\ngovernment irrigation removed\""
    }
  ]
